title: teleport
description: Teleports entities  to specific locations. Can also be written as `/tp`.

fields.title: destination
fields.description: The `vector` [x y z] position to teleport entities to.

fields.title: checkForBlocks
fields.description: A `Boolean` value to prevent teleporting the player if the location they would end up in is occupied by blocks if `true`. Default: `false`.

fields.title: yRot
fields.description: The `float` degrees `y` to rotate a player when teleporting.

fields.title: xRot
fields.description: The `float` degrees `x` to rotate a player when teleporting.

fields.title: lookAtPosition
fields.description: A `vector` [x y z] of where teleported entities should face.

fields.title: lookAtEntity
fields.description: A `string` or [`target selector`](https://learn.microsoft.com/minecraft/creator/documents/commandsintroduction#target-selectors) to identify which `entity` teleported entities should face.

fields.title: victim
fields.description: A `string` or [`target selector`](https://learn.microsoft.com/minecraft/creator/documents/commandsintroduction#target-selectors) to identify which player is teleported.

overloads.title: Teleport self
overloads.description: `Teleport` yourself to a `vector` destination with optional `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport self, x y rotation
overloads.description: `Teleport` yourself to a `vector` destination with optional `y rotation`, `x rotation`, and `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport self, facing position
overloads.description: `Teleport` yourself to a `vector` destination facing a `vector` position with an optional `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport self, facing entity
overloads.description: `Teleport` yourself  to a `vector` destination facing an `entity` with an optional `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport player, x y rotation
overloads.description: `Teleport` a target `player`  to a `vector` destination with optional `y rotation`, `x rotation`, and `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport player
overloads.description: `Teleport` a target `player` to a `vector` destination with optional `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport player, facing position
overloads.description: `Teleport` a target `player` to a `vector` destination facing a `vector` position with an optional `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport player, facing entity
overloads.description: `Teleport` player to a `vector` destination facing a `entity` with an optional `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport player to entity destination
overloads.description: `Teleport` a target `player` to an entity's destination with an optional `check for blocks`.

overloads.title: Teleport player
overloads.description: `Teleport` a target `player` to a `vector` destination with an optional `check for blocks`.
